The latest source code with this fix has bugged out both InlineResponse and InlineResponseClose events.


The DispId attribute needs to be changed for the InlineResponseClose delegate from 64658 to 64662 in: Outlook/EventInterfaces/ExplorerEvents_10.cs


[SupportByVersionAttribute("Outlook", 15)][PreserveSig, MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.InternalCall, MethodCodeType = MethodCodeType.Runtime), DispId(<strong>64662</strong>)]void InlineResponseClose();
